LensHH-LT — Licensing
=====================

LensHH-LT is distributed under a hybrid license. The two components are
licensed separately:

  1. Source code        MIT License (Part 1 below)
  2. Engine binaries    Proprietary, activation required (Part 2 below)

For licensing questions, commercial inquiries, site licenses, or offline
activation tokens, contact:

  Synapse Optics
  https://synapseoptics.com
  support@synapseoptics.com


